{"lemma":"غَضَبُ","slug":"غَضَبُ","root":"غ.ض.ب","root_slug":"غ-ض-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/غ-ض-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"غَضَب","root":"غضب","pos":"N","occurrence_count":14},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["adj","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":8},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n31949","n31950","n31951","n31957"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%BA%D9%8E%D8%B6%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to become angry, to be angry"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to grow passionate for, to defend"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to protect"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to suffer from smallpox"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of غَضِبَ (ḡaḍiba) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"anger","examples":[{"text":"حَرَصَ جُحَا عَلَى تَجَنُّبِ غَضَبِ زَوْجَتِهِ وَمَرَّةً...","english":"Joha was keen to avoid his wife's anger and once ..."}]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"angry, furious, enraged"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"annoyed, irritated"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare Hebrew עָצַב (`atsab, “to hurt, to pain, to anger”)."},"ipa":["/ɣa.dˤi.ba/","/ɣu.dˤi.ba/","/ɣa.dˤab/","/ɣa.dˤib/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n31949","headword_ar":"غَضْبٌ","root":"gDb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) Red (S)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intense in redness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) you say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHomaru gaDobN","text_ar":"اَحْمَرُ غَضْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": so says ISk: (S:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaDobN","text_ar":"غَضْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHomaru gaDobN","text_ar":"اَحْمَرُ غَضْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"red that is dense,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"deep:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TK:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHomaru","text_ar":"اَحْمَرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"red"},{"kind":"text","text":"], applied to anything: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galiyZN","text_ar":"غَلِيظٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thick,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (TA.)       -A2-  Also, and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaDobapN","text_ar":"غَضْبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A hard rock"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"set,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fixed, in a mountain, and differing therefrom:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or the latter signifies thus: or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a hard, round, rock."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O.)       -A3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlgaDobu","text_ar":"الغَضْبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The lion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the bull:"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also [in the latter sense, or perhaps in both senses,] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlgaDuwbu","text_ar":"الغَضُوبُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TK","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n31950","headword_ar":"غَضَبٌ","root":"gDb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"an inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaDiba","text_ar":"غَضِبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (S, Msb, K.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlgaDabu","text_ar":"الغَضَبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~iDaY","text_ar":"الرِّضَى"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K, TA:) it is variously defined: some say that it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a state of excitement of the blood of the heart for the purpose of revenge:"},{"kind":"text","text":"some say that"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pain on account of anything reparable"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaDab","text_ar":"غَضَب"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and for anything irreparable,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asaf","text_ar":"اَسَف"},{"kind":"text","text":": some say that it [is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a passion which"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"includes all that is evil;"},{"kind":"text","text":"wherefore the Prophet, to a man who asked of him a precept, said,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA tagoDabo","text_ar":"لَا تَغْضَبْ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and some say that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlgaDab","text_ar":"الغَضَب"},{"kind":"text","text":"is ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a passion"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"accompanied by an eagerness to obtain revenge;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Algam~","text_ar":"الغَمّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is accompanied by despair of obtaining it: (TA: [see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gayoZN","text_ar":"غَيْظٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) there is a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaDab","text_ar":"غَضَب"},{"kind":"text","text":"that is commended, and a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaDab","text_ar":"غَضَب"},{"kind":"text","text":"that is discommended; the former being that which is for the sake of religion and truth, or right; and the latter being that which is in a wrong case: and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaDab","text_ar":"غَضَب"},{"kind":"text","text":"of God is his disapproving of the conduct of him who disobeys Him, and whom He will therefore punish. (Ibn- 'Arafeh, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n31951","headword_ar":"غَضِبٌ","root":"gDb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaDobaAnu","text_ar":"غَضْبَانُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n31957","headword_ar":"غُضُبٌّ","root":"gDb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}